Tutorial 1:

How do i make myself an owner?

Ok to give you owner rights you must go into data>characters
and find your player name

EXAMPLE:
Your player name = god
You will see an file in the Character file called: "God"

Open it and search for 
[code]right[/code]
Ok you will see something like this
[code]playerrights = 0[/code]

Just easily change the "0" Into 1-4

1 = Moderator
2 = Administrator
3 = Owner
4 = Donator
5 = Hidden admin (NOT on all servers)

Ok so change your playerrights to 3.
Save it and log in again

MAKE SURE THAT YOU WERE LOGGED OUT AT THE MOMENT YOU WERE CHANGING YOUR CHARACTER FILE!!!
otherwise it won't work
No need to compile btw.
This is because it doesn't have to be converted into an class file.

Ok now a list of common questions:

