I give an quick explanation of this.
[code]        c.getItems().addItem(####, *);[/code]
Additem = This says that you are going to add an item to the players inventory.
#### = This stands for the Item ID you want to be added.
* = This stands for amount of the item that have to be added.

You can just change this by removing or adding those items.
