Tutorial 8

How to change Quest Tab?

Ok first go to your Client.java.

Pres ctrl+F and search for this:
[code]public void clearQInterface[/code]
You will see something like this (DEPENDS ON WHAT SOURCE U USE)
[code]		public void clearQInterface() {
		for(int iD = 29172; iD <= 29264;iD++){
			getPA().sendFrame126("", iD);
		}
		getPA().sendFrame126("@whi@"+ Config.SERVER_NAME +": "+PlayerHandler.getPlayerCount()+" @whi@Online", 29155); //Tab Title
		getPA().sendFrame126(""+ Config.SERVER_NAME +" Options:", 663);

		getPA().sendFrame126("@whi@Owners @gre@Co-Owner", 29161); //1st section title
			getPA().sendFrame126("@whi@"+ Config.OWNER +" @gre@"+ Config.CO_OWNER +"", 29162); //1rd section content

		getPA().sendFrame126("Pk Points: "+pkPoints+"", 29163); //2nd section title

	}[/code]
Now i will explain some of these codes
[code]+PlayerHandler.getPlayerCount()+" @whi@Online[/code]
This will tell how many players are online.
[code]getPA().sendFrame126("@whi@"+ Config.OWNER +" @gre@"+ Config.CO_OWNER +"", 29162);[/code]
This will tell who the owner and co owner is. (It says config.OWNER because in this source the owner and co owner are in config.java)
You can make it just like this aswell
[code]getPA().sendFrame126("@whi@"YOURNAME" @gre@"+ YOURCOOWNERNAME"", 29162);[/code]

For example your owner is named: LALA and your Co owner is named: Gay
Then it will become:
[code]getPA().sendFrame126("@whi@"LALA" @gre@"+ Gay"", 29162);[/code]
Ok this code means:
[code]getPA().sendFrame126("Pk Points: "+pkPoints+"", 29163);[/code]
That it will show your pk points.
You can just add there what you like


